5. The device of claim 1,
wherein performing the lateral view analysis on the character data includes locating characteristic points on the first and second contours of a character of the one or more characters, including dividing the character into segments of more than one size, wherein a characteristic point is located in each segment on the first contour and the second contour of the character;
wherein the computing device is further configured to generate a feature vector of the character based on the lateral view analysis;
wherein identifying the one or more characters includes identifying the character based on the feature vector; and
