locating characteristic points on the first and second contours of a character of the one or more characters; and
dividing the character into segments of more than one size, wherein a characteristic point is located in each segment on the first contour and the second contour of the character;

wherein the method further comprises:
generating, by the device, a feature vector of the character based on the lateral view analysis;

wherein identifying the one or more characters includes identifying the character based on the feature vector; and
wherein the feature vector comprises:
a minimum distance of characteristic points on the first contour of the character;
a maximum distance of characteristic points on the second contour of the character;
a width of the character; and
a height of the character.
